Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,Chapter,0,0,0,,#Sponsors
Comment: 0,0:00:03.02,0:00:03.02,Default,Chapter,0,0,0,,Intro
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.85,0:00:06.02,Default,Narrator,80,80,80,,These kids are called Riders.{NOTE:少年達はライダー。}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.02,0:00:09.44,Default,Narrator,80,80,80,,And they form kinship with monsters.{NOTE:モンスターと絆を結びし者たちである。}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.44,0:00:14.86,Default,Narrator,80,80,80,,But, suddenly, a member of the Ebon Riders,\NGale, has appeared before Lute.{NOTE:突如リュートの前に姿を現した、ブラックライダーズのメンバーゲイル。}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.86,0:00:17.74,Default,Narrator,80,80,80,,Flying a rare Rathalos species empowered by the Rite of Channeling…{NOTE:ゲイルはリュートの絆石を奪うべく…}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.74,0:00:21.04,Default,Narrator,80,80,80,,…Gale tried to seize Lute's Kinship Stone!{NOTE:…伝承の儀で強化した、リオレウス希少種を操り…}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.04,0:00:23.71,Default,Narrator,80,80,80,,There was no end to his merciless attacks.{NOTE:…怒濤の攻撃を仕掛けてくる。}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.71,0:00:29.46,Default,Narrator,80,80,80,,Overwhelmed by Gale and Dusk's strength, Lute was forced to escape.{NOTE:圧倒的な強さを見せつけられたリュートは退散を余儀なくされる。}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.46,0:00:34.30,Default,Narrator,80,80,80,,Back at the village, Chief Omna shared certain lore.{NOTE:村へ戻ったリュートたちにオムナ村長は ある助言を与える。}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.30,0:00:37.30,Default,Omna,0,0,0,,You need to go see the Channeler, Lute.{NOTE:伝承ジイさんの元へ行くのだ、リュート。}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.30,0:00:39.35,Default,Omna,0,0,0,,Take Cheval with you.{NOTE:そしてシュヴァルもじゃ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.35,0:00:43.31,Default,Narrator,80,80,80,,Lute's group managed to get to Darj Snowfields, but…{NOTE:リュートたちは無事タルジュ雪原に到着したが…}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.31,0:00:45.29,Default,Narrator,80,80,80,,…back in Hakum, a crisis unfolds.{NOTE:…そのころハクム村では…}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.73,0:00:50.02,Default,Citizen A,0,0,0,,They lost their Kinship Stones?{NOTE:絆石が奪われるなんて…}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.02,0:00:52.28,Default,Citizen B,0,0,0,,They won't be able to ride Monsties anymore?{NOTE:オトモンに乗ることもできない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.28,0:00:56.45,Default,Citizen C,0,0,0,,Who's going to protect the village if we're attacked?{NOTE:連中が襲ってきたら誰が村を守るんじゃ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.91,0:01:00.08,Default,Beats,0,0,0,,H-Hey!{NOTE:お、おい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.08,0:01:01.79,Default,Beats,0,0,0,,Where are you going?{NOTE:どこへ行く気だ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.79,0:01:03.16,Default,Loloa,0,0,0,,Nariki!{NOTE:ナリキ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.96,0:01:07.92,Default,Omna,0,0,0,,Stay calm, everyone.{NOTE:みんな、落ち着くのじゃ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.92,0:01:13.59,Default,Omna,0,0,0,,I'm sure we all remember the days when we faced the Black Blight.{NOTE:一丸となって黒の凶気に立ち向かった日のことを思い出すのじゃ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.59,0:01:18.09,Default,Omna,0,0,0,,As long as we don't give up, hope won't abandon us.{NOTE:諦めないかぎり希望はわれらを見捨てん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.09,0:01:20.60,Default,Citizen D,0,0,0,,Let's defend the village by ourselves!{NOTE:俺たちの手で村を守り抜こう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.60,0:01:23.68,Default,Citzen E,0,0,0,,Even if they took our Kinship Stones, they can't take the village's kinship!{NOTE:絆石を奪われようが村の絆は固い！}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.68,0:01:26.48,Default,Citzen F,0,0,0,,Let's not forget the pride of Hakum village!{NOTE:ハクム村の誇りを忘れるな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.48,0:01:28.27,Default,Mille,0,0,0,,We've got to do something too.{NOTE:私たちも何かしなくちゃ。 }
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.27,0:01:29.94,Default,Hyoro,0,0,0,,What do you have in mind?{NOTE:何かって？}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.07,0:01:33.40,Default,Mille,0,0,0,,Even Lute was beat by those riders.{NOTE:リュートがあそこまでやられたのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.40,0:01:37.41,Default,Mille,0,0,0,,It's pathetic, but we don't stand a chance against them.{NOTE:悔しいけど今の私たちには太刀打ちできないわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.41,0:01:41.45,Default,Floof,0,0,0,,Mille-Mille, I also want to do something useful-nyaa.{NOTE:ミルミル、僕も何かお役に立ちたいでしゅニャ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.45,0:01:42.54,Default,Mille,0,0,0,,Floof-floof…{NOTE:チャモチャモ…}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.54,0:01:45.96,Default,Floof,0,0,0,,My sigh can put them to sleep.{NOTE:僕は吐息でみんなを眠らせられるでしゅニャ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.96,0:01:48.46,Default,Floof,0,0,0,,See for yourself.{NOTE:ほら。ハァ～。}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.38,0:02:00.35,Default,Mille,0,0,0,,T-Too cute!{NOTE:カ…カワイイ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.72,0:02:03.35,Default,Mille,0,0,0,,W-What?{NOTE:な…何よ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.35,0:02:05.68,Default,Hyoro,0,0,0,,Hehe. Oh, nothing.{NOTE:フフフ。別に。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.68,0:02:09.90,Default,Hyoro,0,0,0,,But I have been thinking about what we can do.{NOTE:それより今の僕たちにできることを考えたんだけど。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.90,0:02:11.98,Default,Mille,0,0,0,,And?{NOTE:何？}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.98,0:02:15.03,Default,Hyoro,0,0,0,,Let's search for a new Monstie!{NOTE:新しいオトモンを探そう。}
