Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.89,0:02:32.19,OP/ED English,,0,0,0,,We are still living today{NOTE:僕ら今日も生きている}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.19,0:02:35.42,OP/ED English,,0,0,0,,We are still laughing today{NOTE:僕ら今日も笑ってる}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.42,0:02:39.92,OP/ED English,,0,0,0,,We don't need anything more{NOTE:それだけでもう何もいらない}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.92,0:02:41.79,OP/ED English,,0,0,0,,Just RIDE ON{NOTE:今すぐRIDE ON}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.79,0:02:45.09,OP/ED English,,0,0,0,,We're quick to want{NOTE:僕らすぐに求める}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.09,0:02:48.29,OP/ED English,,0,0,0,,This feeling is only natural{NOTE:欲張りな生き物さ}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.29,0:02:54.32,OP/ED English,,0,0,0,,We're born without anything after all{NOTE:何も持たずに生まれてきたのに}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.32,0:02:56.09,OP/ED English,,0,0,0,,Happiness is{NOTE:幸せは}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.09,0:02:59.16,OP/ED English,,0,0,0,,To be by your side, to be close to you{NOTE:そばにあって　近くにあって}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.16,0:03:02.56,OP/ED English,,0,0,0,,Not to lose sight of what is really important{NOTE:大切なものほど見えなくなるけど}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.56,0:03:03.86,OP/ED English,,0,0,0,,To be grateful{NOTE:感謝して}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.86,0:03:08.89,OP/ED English,,0,0,0,,To the person who understands no matter what happens{NOTE:何が起きたって分かってくれる人へ}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.89,0:03:11.89,OP/ED English,,0,0,0,,Everyone is afraid{NOTE:誰にだって　逃げたくなって}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.89,0:03:15.32,OP/ED English,,0,0,0,,To lose sight of oneself{NOTE:自分を見失いそうになるけど}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.32,0:03:23.29,OP/ED English,,0,0,0,,But you will surely find love in your heart{NOTE:愛は必ず君の心にあるよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.29,0:03:28.52,OP/ED English,,0,0,0,,Come walk with us{NOTE:僕ら一緒に歩いていこうよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.52,0:03:34.12,OP/ED English,,0,0,0,,We're under the same sky, we look at the same stars{NOTE:同じ空のした　同じ空を見上げながら}
