Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.79,0:04:38.04,Default,Loloa,0,0,0,,Nariki, wait!{NOTE:ナリキ！待ってくださいですの。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.04,0:04:40.15,Default,Beats,0,0,0,,Where are you going, Nariki?{NOTE:どこへ行くつもりなんだナリキ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.51,0:04:44.18,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,I'm going to get their Kinship Stones back.{NOTE:先輩たちの絆石を取り返すっす。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.18,0:04:46.09,Default,Beats,0,0,0,,Huh? All by yourself?{NOTE:はあ!?お前一人で？}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.09,0:04:47.47,Default,Loloa,0,0,0,,That's just reckless.{NOTE:無茶ですの。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.47,0:04:49.58,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,I know it's reckless, but I need to do it.{NOTE:無茶でも何でもやるしかない！}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.47,0:04:54.69,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,I've always looked up to my seniors and Lute.{NOTE:自分はずっとﾘｭｰﾄ先輩たちの背中を見てきた。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.69,0:04:59.73,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,Their power, how they never give up, and how they fight with all they've got, even at the worst times.{NOTE:どんなときも決して諦めず全力で立ち向かう背中を！}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.61,0:05:03.28,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,This time it's my turn to fight.{NOTE:今度は自分が立ち向かう番っす。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.28,0:05:08.45,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,I will get my seniors' Kinship Stones with these two hands!{NOTE:この手で先輩たちの絆石を必ず取り戻してみせるっす。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.45,0:05:09.78,Default,Loloa,0,0,0,,Nariki…{NOTE:ナリキ…}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.78,0:05:11.12,Default,Beats,0,0,0,,Atta boy!{NOTE:よく言った！}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.12,0:05:14.37,Default,Beats,0,0,0,,I'll lend you my hands too!{NOTE:よし！俺のありがたい手を特別に貸してやる！}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.76,0:05:32.22,Default,Hyoro,0,0,0,,This area was supposed to be a monster's den.{NOTE:この辺りはモンスターの巣だったのに。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.22,0:05:33.77,Default,Mille,0,0,0,,Doesn't look like it.{NOTE:ないわね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.35,0:05:36.89,Default,Spex,0,0,0,,Something's coming.{NOTE:何か来るゴロニャ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.89,0:05:37.85,Default,(unison),0,0,0,,Huh?{NOTE:あっ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.36,0:05:48.95,Default,Mille,0,0,0,,Bnahabra! Let's get out of here!{NOTE:ブナハブラ。逃げるわよ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.95,0:05:49.99,Default,Hyoro,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah!{NOTE:う…うん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.58,0:06:00.92,Default,Mille,0,0,0,,What now?{NOTE:どうしよう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.92,0:06:04.05,Default,Mille,0,0,0,,It'll be impossible to find an egg in the dark.{NOTE:こんなに暗くちゃ卵が探せないわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.05,0:06:06.76,Default,Spex,0,0,0,,Leave it to me.{NOTE:僕に任せてゴロニャ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.30,0:06:13.47,Default,Spex,0,0,0,,Take a look in that grassy place.{NOTE:あの草むらを探すゴロニャ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.27,0:06:23.42,Default,Hyoro,0,0,0,,An egg!{NOTE:卵だ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.15,0:06:25.74,Default,Mille,0,0,0,,You did it, Hyoro!{NOTE:やったわね！ヒョロ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.74,0:06:27.36,Default,Hyoro,0,0,0,,It's yours, Mille.{NOTE:これはミルのだよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.36,0:06:28.11,Default,Mille,0,0,0,,Huh?{NOTE:えっ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.74,0:06:35.79,Default,Mille,0,0,0,,Where did you find this one?{NOTE:あんたいつの間に…}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.79,0:06:38.54,Default,Hyoro,0,0,0,,In the Babda Rainforest.{NOTE:バブダの密林で見つけたんだけど…}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.54,0:06:41.81,Default,Hyoro,0,0,0,,But I wanted to open it with you, Mille.{NOTE:…絆あわせはミルと一緒にやろうって決めてたから。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.88,0:06:43.82,Default,Mille,0,0,0,,Hyoro…{NOTE:ヒョロ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.30,0:06:47.13,Default,Hyoro,0,0,0,,Let's awaken our Monsties together.{NOTE:一緒に新しいオトモンを目覚めさせよう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.13,0:06:47.94,Default,Mille,0,0,0,,Okay.{NOTE:うん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.22,0:06:51.30,Default,(unison),0,0,0,,O' holy Kinship Stone…{NOTE:聖なる絆石よ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.30,0:06:54.58,Default,(unison),0,0,0,,…bind thou together our's and these slumbering souls.\N{NOTE:われと眠りしみ霊の絆を結びたまえ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.97,0:06:57.35,Default,(unison),0,0,0,,And now, the moment of new life:{NOTE:いざ新生の時…}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.35,0:06:58.33,Default,(unison),0,0,0,,Awaken!{NOTE:…目覚めよ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.65,0:07:06.67,Default,Hyoro,0,0,0,,Wow, it's a Zinogre!{NOTE:わあ、ジンオウガだ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.03,0:07:14.22,Default,Hyoro,0,0,0,,A Thousand Blade Wyvern, Seregios!{NOTE:千刃竜セルレギオス。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.45,0:07:21.04,Default,Spex,0,0,0,,Oh, Floof also woke up.{NOTE:チャモも目覚めたゴロニャ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.04,0:07:23.58,Default,Spex,0,0,0,,You should name them.{NOTE:名前をつけるといいゴロニャ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.58,0:07:27.23,Default,Spex,0,0,0,,It will deepen the kinship between you,\Njust like with Lute and Ratha.{NOTE:リュートとレウスみたいに絆がさらに深まるゴロニャ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.49,0:07:33.11,Default,Hyoro,0,0,0,,You're a Zinogre, so how about Zinrai?{NOTE:ジンオウガだからジンライってどうかな？}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.49,0:07:36.26,Sign,,0,0,0,,Zinrai (じんらい) means thunderclap (迅雷).
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.01,0:07:36.26,Default,Spex,0,0,0,,It has a nice ring to it.{NOTE:いい響きゴロニャ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.26,0:07:39.02,Default,Mille,0,0,0,,This girl here is a Seregios, so let's go with Legion.{NOTE:この子はセルレギオスだからレギオン。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.02,0:07:41.27,Default,Floof,0,0,0,,A very noble name-nyaa.{NOTE:すてきな名前でしゅニャ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.27,0:07:42.98,Default,Floof,0,0,0,,She looks happy about it.{NOTE:喜んでましゅニャ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.98,0:07:44.61,Default,Hyoro,0,0,0,,Let's be good friends, Zinrai.{NOTE:よろしくね、ジンライ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.61,0:07:46.52,Default,Mille,0,0,0,,It's nice to meet you, Legion.{NOTE:よろしく、レギオン。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.52,0:07:47.90,Default,Loloa,0,0,0,,We've got trouble!{NOTE:大変ですの。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.90,0:07:49.15,Default,Hyoro,0,0,0,,Loloa.{NOTE:ロロア。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.86,0:07:52.57,Default,Loloa,0,0,0,,Nariki left the village all by himself…!{NOTE:ナリキが一人で村の外に…}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.57,0:07:53.47,Default,(unison),0,0,0,,Eh?{NOTE:あっ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.37,0:08:00.64,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,Excuse me!{NOTE:すみませ～ん！}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.71,0:08:06.67,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,Have you seen anybody that looks like this?{NOTE:こんな人たち通り掛からなかったっすか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.67,0:08:09.92,Default,Beats,0,0,0,,They're kidnapping pretty girls\Nand snatching Kinship Stones.{NOTE:美少女をさらったり絆石を奪ったり…}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.92,0:08:12.03,Default,Beats,0,0,0,,They just do whatever they want.{NOTE:…やりたい放題の連中なんだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.93,0:08:15.64,Default,Mad,0,0,0,,This doesn't bear the slightest resemblance.{NOTE:似ても似つかない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.64,0:08:17.22,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,E-Eh? To what?{NOTE:えっ？何すか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.97,0:08:20.06,Default,Mad,0,0,0,,To us, the Ebon Riders.{NOTE:わがブラックライダーズは…}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.06,0:08:23.23,Default,Mad,0,0,0,,We're an indestructible group\Nwielding unquestionable strength.{NOTE:…究極の強さを誇る不滅の集団。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.23,0:08:26.23,Default,Mad,0,0,0,,This depiction is a blasphemy.{NOTE:こんな醜いやからではありません。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.23,0:08:29.19,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,E-Ebon Riders?{NOTE:ブ…ブラックライダーズ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.19,0:08:29.75,Default,Mad,0,0,0,,Heh.{NOTE:フッ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.19,0:08:35.53,Default,Mad,0,0,0,,Right now, you're standing before an unprecedented\Nbeauty that makes everyone's heart pound…{NOTE:空前絶後の美貌で見る者全てを恋に狂わせる…}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.53,0:08:38.45,Default,Mad,0,0,0,,…one of the unrivaled four Ebon Riders.{NOTE:…ブラックライダーズ四天王が一人…}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.45,0:08:41.10,Default,Mad,0,0,0,,Mad is my name.{NOTE:…マッドさまとは私のこと。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.04,0:08:43.75,Default,Mad,0,0,0,,Take extreme caution.{NOTE:ご用心あれ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.75,0:08:46.67,Default,Mad,0,0,0,,If you fall in love with me, you'll get burned.{NOTE:私にほれたらやけどしますよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.17,0:08:50.13,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,He's kinda creepy, but…{NOTE:何かキモいんすけど。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.13,0:08:51.80,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,…I expected someone more scary.{NOTE:もっと怖いやつらだと…}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.80,0:08:54.84,Default,Beats,0,0,0,,This guy is dangerous.\NIt's better not to get involved with his type.{NOTE:こいつはヤバい。関わっちゃいけないタイプだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.84,0:08:56.05,Default,Beats,0,0,0,,In many ways.{NOTE:いろんな意味で。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.59,0:08:57.72,Default,Mad,0,0,0,,Heh.{NOTE:フッ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.72,0:09:03.48,Default,Mad,0,0,0,,It seems you possess a beautiful Kinship Stone.{NOTE:美しい絆石をお持ちですね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.48,0:09:07.90,Default,Mad,0,0,0,,A beautiful Kinship Stone deserves\Na beautiful hand to wield it.{NOTE:美しい絆石にふさわしいのは美しい腕です。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.90,0:09:10.15,Default,Mad,0,0,0,,For example, a hand such as this.{NOTE:例えばこの腕のように。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.03,0:09:12.90,Default,Beats,0,0,0,,Nariki!{NOTE:ナリキ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.90,0:09:16.16,Default,Mad,0,0,0,,I will kindly take that Kinship Stone.{NOTE:その絆石私が頂いてあげます。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.16,0:09:19.58,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,Let go of me!\NI'll never give anything to a creep like you!{NOTE:放せ。お前なんかに絶対渡すもんか！}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.58,0:09:22.41,Default,Mad,0,0,0,,What an unattractive attitude.{NOTE:その態度は美しくないですよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.41,0:09:24.14,Default,Beats,0,0,0,,Let go of Nariki!{NOTE:ナリキよけろ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.29,0:09:26.17,Default,Mad,0,0,0,,Ah, it's hot!{NOTE:熱っ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.17,0:09:27.15,Default,Beats,0,0,0,,Go! Nariki!{NOTE:いけ！ナリキ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.67,0:09:29.17,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,Ride On!{NOTE:ライドオン！}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.09,0:09:32.15,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,Velocidrome!{NOTE:ドスランポス！}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.80,0:09:44.54,Default,Mad,0,0,0,,The ugliest thing in the world is useless resistance.{NOTE:この世で一番醜いものは無駄な悪あがきですよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.89,0:09:49.06,Default,Beats,0,0,0,,'Aight! We're losing him!{NOTE:よっしゃ。振り切ったぞ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.06,0:09:51.61,Default,Beats,0,0,0,,That's the strong legs of a Velocidrome for ya!{NOTE:さすが脚力自慢のドスランポス！}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.69,0:09:55.69,Default,Beats,0,0,0,,Something's coming!{NOTE:ん？何か来るぞ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.92,0:10:11.42,Default,Beats,0,0,0,,The Red Devil.{NOTE:赤い悪魔。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.42,0:10:12.92,Default,Beats,0,0,0,,Khezu species.{NOTE:フルフル亜種。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.92,0:10:15.84,Default,Mad,0,0,0,,I am a merciful man.{NOTE:私は慈悲深い人間です。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.84,0:10:19.18,Default,Mad,0,0,0,,So in my benevolence,\Nyou'll be given one more chance.{NOTE:もう一度だけチャンスをあげましょう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.18,0:10:21.39,Default,Mad,0,0,0,,Relinquish your Kinship Stone.{NOTE:絆石を差し出しなさい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.39,0:10:22.93,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,Who would give it to someone like you?{NOTE:誰が渡すか！}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.93,0:10:24.10,Default,Mad,0,0,0,,Oh my.{NOTE:やれやれ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.10,0:10:25.89,Default,Mad,0,0,0,,You're one ungrateful boy.{NOTE:聞き分けのない坊やだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.89,0:10:32.40,Default,Mad,0,0,0,,My beautiful Monstie, Fool, is particularly\Ngood at handling disobedient children.{NOTE:私の美しいオトモンフールは子供の扱いがとても上手なんですよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.40,0:10:34.73,Default,Mad,0,0,0,,I'm sure you'll enjoy his lovely cuddles.{NOTE:たっぷりかわいがってもらいなさい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.12,0:10:44.41,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,Beats-Senpai!{NOTE:ビーツ先輩！}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.41,0:10:46.75,Default,Beats,0,0,0,,Save your thanks for later.{NOTE:礼なら後でたっぷり聞いてやる。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.75,0:10:48.50,Default,Beats,0,0,0,,We've gotta scram!{NOTE:今はとにかく回避に徹しろ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.50,0:10:49.54,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,Roger that!{NOTE:はいっす！}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.96,0:11:01.47,Default,Mad,0,0,0,,I thought this might turn out to be a good exercise,\Nbut we've only burnt about 30 kilo calories…{NOTE:いいエクササイズになるかと思いましたが消費できたのは30キロカロリー程度でしょうか。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.47,0:11:03.85,Default,Mad,0,0,0,,What a trifling hunt.{NOTE:つまらない狩りでした。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.85,0:11:06.89,Default,Mad,0,0,0,,Fool, would you be so kind to deal the finishing blow?{NOTE:フール、とどめを刺してさしあげなさい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.35,0:11:12.23,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,– Damn! Step on it!\N– No need to tell me twice!{NOTE:—ヤバいぞ！逃げろ！\\N—分かってますって。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.23,0:11:14.40,Default,Mad,0,0,0,,It's the finale you've all been awaiting.{NOTE:お待ちかねのフィナーレです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.40,0:11:16.38,Default,Mad,0,0,0,,Thunder Breath!{NOTE:豪雷ブレス！}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.32,0:11:21.78,Default,Beats,0,0,0,,A Seregios?{NOTE:セルレギオス！}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.78,0:11:22.66,Default,Mille,0,0,0,,Nariki!{NOTE:ナリキ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.66,0:11:23.82,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,Mille!{NOTE:ミル先輩！}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.82,0:11:24.64,Default,Mille,0,0,0,,Get down!{NOTE:下がって！}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.83,0:11:27.14,Default,Mille,0,0,0,,Legion! Now!{NOTE:レギオン！今よ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.96,0:11:32.71,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,Awesome! That's our Mille!{NOTE:すごい。さすがミル先輩っす。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.71,0:11:34.34,Default,Beats,0,0,0,,She got it going on!{NOTE:やるじゃねえか！}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.34,0:11:36.55,Default,Hyoro,0,0,0,,We don't have time for compliments!{NOTE:感心してる場合じゃないよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.55,0:11:38.76,Default,Hyoro,0,0,0,,Take this chance to get away, Nariki!{NOTE:今のうちに逃げて、ナリキ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.76,0:11:40.42,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,Thank you!{NOTE:ありがとうございます！}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.05,0:11:42.72,Default,Mad,0,0,0,,Hmph. How impudent.{NOTE:フッ。フッこしゃくな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.72,0:11:43.89,Default,Mad,0,0,0,,Fool.{NOTE:フール。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.89,0:11:46.60,Default,Mad,0,0,0,,Please show them the difference in our power.{NOTE:力の差を見せつけておやりなさい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.60,0:11:48.35,Default,Mad,0,0,0,,Thunder Breath!{NOTE:豪雷ブレス！}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.81,0:11:53.19,Default,Mille,0,0,0,,Legion!{NOTE:レギオン！}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.02,0:11:58.98,Default,Mad,0,0,0,,Oh? Did I say "Thunder Breath"?\NSo sorry, that was actually a Thunder Trap.{NOTE:今のは豪雷ブレスと見せ掛けて正解はサンダートラップです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.98,0:12:03.45,Default,Mad,0,0,0,,It's a complex attack that lower life forms\Nsuch as yourself couldn't possibly understand.{NOTE:単細胞のあなた方にはできない複雑な攻撃です。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.57,0:12:06.87,Default,Hyoro,0,0,0,,Mille, leave this to Zinrai.{NOTE:ミル、ここはジンライに任せて。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.41,0:12:11.21,Default,Spex,0,0,0,,Khezu species use the thunder attacks.{NOTE:フルフル亜種は雷属性ゴロニャ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.21,0:12:15.25,Default,Spex,0,0,0,,And so do Zinogres,\Nso they have a higher resistance to it.{NOTE:同じ雷属性のジンオウガは耐性があるゴロニャ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.25,0:12:16.92,Default,Mille,0,0,0,,I guess you're right.{NOTE:分かったわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.92,0:12:19.55,Default,Mille,0,0,0,,Legion, we'll cover for them from a distance.{NOTE:レギオン私たちは援護に回るわよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.88,0:12:23.55,Default,Mad,0,0,0,,No matter who comes, the result remains the same.{NOTE:どなたが来ようと結果は同じ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.55,0:12:26.76,Default,Mad,0,0,0,,Your chaotic disperse is unsightly.{NOTE:あなた方はここでぶざまに散るのです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.76,0:12:28.12,Default,Mille,0,0,0,,Legion! Cover them!{NOTE:レギオン！援護よ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.47,0:12:31.45,Default,Mille,0,0,0,,That's it!{NOTE:その調子！}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.73,0:12:33.73,Default,Beats,0,0,0,,Alright!{NOTE:よっしゃ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.73,0:12:35.38,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,Yeah, nice assist!{NOTE:ナイスアシストっす！}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.19,0:12:41.03,Default,Mad,0,0,0,,Shall I draw a line here for our warm up?{NOTE:ウオーミングアップはこのくらいにしておきましょうか。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.03,0:12:44.11,Default,Mad,0,0,0,,It is about time we got serious.{NOTE:そろそろ本気でいかせていただきますよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.24,0:12:46.95,Default,Mad,0,0,0,,Sync Ride!{NOTE:シンクライド！}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.26,0:13:03.05,Default,Beats,0,0,0,,What is that movement?{NOTE:何だ？あの動き。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.05,0:13:04.11,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,He's creeping me out.{NOTE:気持ち悪っ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.55,0:13:10.97,Default,Mad,0,0,0,,It's overflowing! The power's overflowing!{NOTE:みなぎる！力がみなぎる！}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.97,0:13:12.22,Default,Mille,0,0,0,,What's with him?{NOTE:何なの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.22,0:13:15.14,Default,Floof,0,0,0,,He and his Khezu synced their movements-nyaa.{NOTE:フルフルの動きとシンクロしてるでしゅニャ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.65,0:13:19.82,Default,Mad,0,0,0,,It's understandable that you're scared out of your wits.{NOTE:われわれの本気に度肝を抜かれるがいい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.82,0:13:23.24,Default,Mad,0,0,0,,Fool! Ice Cyclone!{NOTE:フール！アイスサイクロン！}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.24,0:13:24.86,Default,Hyoro,0,0,0,,Ice Cyclone!?{NOTE:アイスサイクロン!?}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.86,0:13:27.84,Default,Spex,0,0,0,,How can a Khezu use ice attacks!?{NOTE:なぜフルフル亜種が氷属性の技を!?}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.63,0:13:43.17,Default,Beats,0,0,0,,What's with that speed?{NOTE:な…何だ？あのスピードは。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.96,0:13:46.09,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,What's going on?{NOTE:いったいどうなって…。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.09,0:13:47.76,Default,Mad,0,0,0,,Yahoo!{NOTE:いやっほ～！}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.76,0:13:49.72,Default,Mad,0,0,0,,The real battle is about to start now.{NOTE:本番はこれからだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.72,0:13:53.93,Default,Mad,0,0,0,,It'll be a beautiful and cruel show.{NOTE:私とフールの美しくも残酷なショーのね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.77,0:13:58.00,Default,Mad,0,0,0,,Look forward to it.{NOTE:ご期待あれ。}
Comment: 0,0:13:58.06,0:13:58.06,Default,Chapter,0,0,0,,Eyecatch
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.60,0:13:59.94,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,Ride On!{NOTE:ライドオン！}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.90,0:14:01.94,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,Rathalos!{NOTE:リオレウス！}
Comment: 0,0:14:02.07,0:14:02.07,Default,Chapter,0,0,0,,#Black screen
Comment: 0,0:14:04.07,0:14:04.07,Default,Chapter,0,0,0,,$Eyecatch
Comment: 0,0:14:08.07,0:14:08.07,Default,Chapter,0,0,0,,Part B
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.53,0:14:10.74,Default,Hyoro,0,0,0,,Zinrai!{NOTE:ジンライ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.74,0:14:11.70,Default,Hyoro,0,0,0,,Are you okay?{NOTE:大丈夫？}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.70,0:14:12.72,Default,Hyoro,0,0,0,,Hang in there!{NOTE:しっかりして！}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.54,0:14:15.37,Default,Spex,0,0,0,,Hyoro, behind you!{NOTE:ヒョロさん！危ないゴロニャ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.37,0:14:17.44,Default,Mad,0,0,0,,Frozen Breath!{NOTE:凍結ブレス！}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.67,0:14:20.71,Default,Mille,0,0,0,,Legion!{NOTE:レギオン！}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.34,0:14:24.17,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,Khezu are supposed to use thunder attacks, right?{NOTE:フルフル亜種は雷属性なんすよね？}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.17,0:14:27.22,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,So how can it use an ice attack?{NOTE:なのにどうして氷属性の攻撃を？}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.22,0:14:31.85,Default,Beats,0,0,0,,They must have used the Rite of Channeling.{NOTE:きっと伝承の儀とやらで氷属性のスキルを身につけたんだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.85,0:14:33.39,Default,Beats,0,0,0,,This is tough.{NOTE:こりゃ手ごわいぞ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.81,0:14:37.85,Default,Beats,0,0,0,,You can't fight on this level yet.{NOTE:今のお前に太刀打ちできる相手じゃねえ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.85,0:14:39.40,Default,Beats,0,0,0,,We should retreat!{NOTE:ひとまず退散するぞ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.40,0:14:41.31,Default,Beats,0,0,0,,Nariki!{NOTE:ナリキ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.31,0:14:45.36,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,I can't abandon my seniors and run away by myself!{NOTE:先輩たちを見捨てて自分だけ逃げるなんてできないっす！}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.36,0:14:48.09,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,There must be something I can do for them!{NOTE:きっとあるはず。自分にもできることが。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.32,0:14:54.28,Default,Beats,0,0,0,,What's so special about this sap plant?{NOTE:ネンチャク草がどうかしたのか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.58,0:14:58.29,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,Beats-Senpai, please get us some stones.{NOTE:ビーツ先輩石を集めてください。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.29,0:15:00.17,Default,Beats,0,0,0,,Are you nuts? What for?{NOTE:石ころ拾ってる場合かよ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.17,0:15:02.13,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,Also get some monster's poop.{NOTE:あとモンスターのふんも。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.13,0:15:04.59,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,– Huh!?\N– Please hurry up!{NOTE:—はあ!?\\N—急いでください。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.59,0:15:06.55,Default,Beats,0,0,0,,A-Alright, whatever!{NOTE:わ-分かったよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.05,0:15:15.18,Default,Mad,0,0,0,,It's time to settle this and get those Kinship Stones.{NOTE:一気に片を付けて絆石を根こそぎ頂くよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.18,0:15:17.93,Default,Mad,0,0,0,,Fool, do your beautiful thing!{NOTE:フール。やっちゃって～。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.93,0:15:22.23,Default,Mad,0,0,0,,This time, it's the true finale!{NOTE:今度こそお待ちかねのフィナーレだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.23,0:15:24.61,Default,Mad,0,0,0,,Extended Frozen Breath!{NOTE:拡散凍結ブレ～ス！}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.61,0:15:26.98,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,Eat this!{NOTE:これでも食らえ～！}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.99,0:15:32.61,Default,Mad,0,0,0,,W-What's that stench?{NOTE:な-何だこの臭いは。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.61,0:15:35.70,Default,Mad,0,0,0,,How repugnant! My nose is in distress!{NOTE:実に醜い！鼻が曲がる！}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.70,0:15:36.66,Default,Beats,0,0,0,,Hehe!{NOTE:ヘヘ～。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.66,0:15:40.16,Default,Beats,0,0,0,,It's a ball of fertilizer filled with monster poop!{NOTE:モンスターのふんを調合したこやし玉さ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.46,0:15:49.09,Default,Mad,0,0,0,,My beautiful face confronted with m-m-monster poop…!{NOTE:私の美しい顔にモンスターのふんが～。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.01,0:15:53.05,Default,Mad,0,0,0,,This is a terrible situation that should not exist!{NOTE:これはあってはならない由々しき事態。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.05,0:15:54.72,Default,Mad,0,0,0,,I need to take a shower!{NOTE:すぐに熱いシャワーで…}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.72,0:15:58.43,Default,Mad,0,0,0,,I have to wash immediately! Fool, we're leaving!{NOTE:…洗い流さなくては！フール行きますよ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.43,0:16:00.14,Default,Spex,0,0,0,,He left.{NOTE:逃げたゴロニャ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.14,0:16:01.77,Default,Floof,0,0,0,,It stinks-nyaa.{NOTE:くしゃいでしゅニャ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.94,0:16:05.73,Default,Beats,0,0,0,,Khezu can't see…{NOTE:フルフルは目が見えない分…}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.73,0:16:07.98,Default,Beats,0,0,0,,…but their sense of smell is amazing.{NOTE:…嗅覚がすごいからな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.98,0:16:10.44,Default,Beats,0,0,0,,That level of stench was way too intense for it.{NOTE:こやし玉は強烈だったろうな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.44,0:16:12.36,Default,Beats,0,0,0,,Atta boy, Nariki!{NOTE:よくやった、ナリキ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.36,0:16:15.32,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,Hehe. Please don't praise me too much.{NOTE:エヘヘ。そんな褒めないでくださいよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.32,0:16:17.16,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,It was just a fluke.{NOTE:まぐれっすよまぐれ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.16,0:16:21.87,Default,Mille,0,0,0,,Listen here! What were you thinking,\Nleaving the village all on your own?{NOTE:あのね！一人で勝手に村の外に出るなんて何考えてるのよ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.87,0:16:25.63,Default,Mille,0,0,0,,What if we hadn't shown in time? Huh? What then?{NOTE:私たちが駆け付けなかったら今ごろどうなってたか。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.63,0:16:28.00,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,But it ended up fine, didn't it?{NOTE:でも結果オーライだったじゃないっすか～。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.00,0:16:29.38,Default,Mille,0,0,0,,That's not the point…!{NOTE:そういう問題じゃない！}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.38,0:16:31.55,Default,Hyoro,0,0,0,,Now, now, don't be so mad.{NOTE:まあまあそのくらいで。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.55,0:16:35.01,Default,Hyoro,0,0,0,,Thanks to Nariki we still have our Kinship Stones.{NOTE:ナリキのおかげで絆石は奪われずに済んだんだし。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.51,0:16:38.33,Default,Hyoro,0,0,0,,Thank you, Nariki.{NOTE:ありがとう、ナリキ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.93,0:16:43.48,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,I'm glad I could be of some use.{NOTE:エヘヘヘ。お役に立てて何よりっす。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.48,0:16:44.60,Default,Mille,0,0,0,,Geez.{NOTE:フゥ…}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.44,0:16:49.44,Default,Mille,0,0,0,,Well, if we want to get the rest of the Kinship Stones back…{NOTE:私たちはダン先輩たちの絆石を取り戻すために…}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.44,0:16:51.90,Default,Mille,0,0,0,,…we should head back to the\hvillage and prepare for departure.{NOTE:…いったん村へ戻って準備をするわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.90,0:16:53.95,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,I'm going with you!{NOTE:自分も行くっす！}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.95,0:16:55.86,Default,Mille,0,0,0,,Nope, it's the village for you.{NOTE:あんたは村に残りなさい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.86,0:16:59.20,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,But why? Please take me along.{NOTE:え～？自分も連れていってくださいよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.20,0:16:59.79,Default,Mille,0,0,0,,No!{NOTE:駄目！}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.79,0:17:01.25,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,Come on…{NOTE:そんな～。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.25,0:17:05.79,Default,Hyoro,0,0,0,,I understand how you feel,\Nbut you just became a Rider, Nariki.{NOTE:気持ちは分かるけどナリキはライダーになったばかりだし。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.79,0:17:09.55,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,Please, I promise I won't be a burden.{NOTE:お願いします！足手まといにならないって約束します！}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.55,0:17:13.28,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,Please! I just want to do something for the village!{NOTE:自分も村のために少しでも力になりたいっす！}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.38,0:17:15.47,Default,Hyoro,0,0,0,,Nariki…{NOTE:ナリキ…}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.76,0:17:21.43,Default,Beats,0,0,0,,He looks pretty serious if you ask me.{NOTE:どうやらマジみたいだぜ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.43,0:17:25.04,Default,Beats,0,0,0,,Why don't you see how far\Nthat determination takes him?{NOTE:なあ。こいつのやる気にかけてみてもいいんじゃないか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.28,0:17:35.32,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,– If you insist so m—\N– And I already helped you out, didn't I?{NOTE:—しょうがない。\\N—さっきも役に立ったじゃないっすか。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.32,0:17:38.57,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,What do you think would've happened if I hadn't saved you?{NOTE:自分がいなかったら先輩たちはどうなってたか。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.57,0:17:40.33,Default,Mille,0,0,0,,You're the one to talk.{NOTE:自分で言うな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.33,0:17:42.70,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,Hehe, sorry.{NOTE:エヘヘすいません。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.70,0:17:44.29,Default,Mille,0,0,0,,Honestly…{NOTE:まったく…}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.29,0:17:47.50,Default,Mille,0,0,0,,That confidence will get you into trouble some day.{NOTE:その自信が過信じゃないことを祈るわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.50,0:17:50.50,Default,Hyoro,0,0,0,,I am still afraid whenever I leave our village.{NOTE:故郷を離れるのは心細いけど。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.50,0:17:54.51,Default,Hyoro,0,0,0,,But we have our new Monsties.{NOTE:僕たちには絆で結ばれたオトモンと仲間がいる。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.51,0:17:55.97,Default,Hyoro,0,0,0,,So I know it'll be okay.{NOTE:きっと大丈夫だよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.97,0:17:59.18,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,All right! I'll follow you, Hyoro-Senpai!{NOTE:あざっす！ヒョロ先輩についていくっす！}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.18,0:18:00.30,Default,Hyoro,0,0,0,,S…{NOTE:す…}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.30,0:18:03.47,Default,Hyoro,0,0,0,,Mille, did you hear that!?\NHe called me Hyoro-Senpai!{NOTE:ミル！聞いた!?ヒョロ先輩だって。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.47,0:18:06.94,Default,Hyoro,0,0,0,,I never thought this day would come.{NOTE:先輩って呼ばれる日が来るなんて…}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.94,0:18:10.94,Default,Mille,0,0,0,,Hyoro, you've really got to get some more confidence.{NOTE:ヒョロ、あんたはもう少し自信を持ちなさいよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.20,0:18:20.85,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,Sorry to intrude!{NOTE:ごめんくださ～い！}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.70,0:18:25.00,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,W-Whoa! You surprised me!{NOTE:うわっ！びっくりした！}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.00,0:18:26.04,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,Uhm…{NOTE:あの…}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.04,0:18:27.91,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,Is this the person we're looking for?{NOTE:この方が噂の？}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.91,0:18:29.50,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,He's The Riddlemaster.{NOTE:なぞなぞジイさんだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.50,0:18:31.50,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,Or rather The Channeler…?{NOTE:いや、伝承ジイさん？}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.50,0:18:33.30,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,Which one is it?{NOTE:どっちなのだ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.30,0:18:38.72,Default,Riddlemaster,0,0,0,,I am a riddle loving Channeler,\Nknown by some as Dede Geezer.{NOTE:オラはなぞなぞ好きの伝承ジイさんデデ爺だべ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.72,0:18:40.18,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,Alright then, mister.{NOTE:そんじゃデデ爺。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.18,0:18:42.01,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,Can you tell us about Rite of Channeli—{NOTE:俺たちに伝承の儀のことを教えて—}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.01,0:18:45.43,Default,Riddlemaster,0,0,0,,Before that, how about you answer a riddle or two?{NOTE:おめえたちオラとなぞなぞすんべ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.60,0:18:50.85,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,Um, sorry, but we don't have time for that.{NOTE:あ～。悪いけど今はなぞなぞに付き合ってる場合じゃないんだよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.85,0:18:51.94,Default,Riddlemaster,0,0,0,,Oh…?{NOTE:え？}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.19,0:19:00.24,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,He looks so sad.{NOTE:見ていられないくらい悲しそうです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.24,0:19:02.41,Default,Fifi,0,0,0,,Just a little should be okay.{NOTE:少しくらいいいんじゃない？}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.41,0:19:03.89,Default,Fifi,0,0,0,,Let's go along with it.{NOTE:付き合ってあげましょうよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.45,0:19:08.08,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,Fine, I guess we can answer just one.{NOTE:しょうがねえな。分かったよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.87,0:19:11.83,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)}10000 + 10 is…?{NOTE:10000+10は？}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.21,0:19:14.63,Default,Riddlemaster,0,0,0,,What is it, what is it?{NOTE:な～んダ何ダ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.63,0:19:16.88,Default,Riddlemaster,0,0,0,,What is the answer?{NOTE:答えは何ダ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.34,0:19:20.51,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,Let's see… four zeros…{NOTE:えっと…。一十…。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.51,0:19:22.18,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,It's ten thousand. Add ten to it.{NOTE:１万足す10だよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.18,0:19:23.10,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,Oh, right…{NOTE:そっか。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.22,0:19:25.89,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,– How?\N– Eh.{NOTE:で？あ…。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.89,0:19:27.64,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,Lute sucks at arithmetic.{NOTE:リュートは数字に弱い。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.64,0:19:28.98,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,So what if I do!?{NOTE:悪かったな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.98,0:19:30.52,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,I know, I know!{NOTE:あっはい！はい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.52,0:19:33.31,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,The answer is ten thousand ten!{NOTE:分かった！答えはまんじゅう！}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.31,0:19:34.48,Default,Riddlemaster,0,0,0,,Correct.{NOTE:正解ダ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.48,0:19:35.40,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,Hurrah!{NOTE:やったー！}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.40,0:19:36.32,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,As expected from Lilia!{NOTE:さすがリリア！}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.32,0:19:37.53,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,Well done.{NOTE:あっぱれです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.53,0:19:39.07,Default,Fifi,0,0,0,,That was splendid, Lilia.{NOTE:すてきよリリア。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.07,0:19:45.81,Default,Riddlemaster,0,0,0,,As a reward for getting my riddle right,\NI'm giving you this manjū bun.{NOTE:なぞなぞに正解したご褒美にオラの大事な温泉まんじゅうをあげるダ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.07,0:19:45.81,Sign,,0,0,0,,Manjū bun (饅頭) is spelled the same as 10010 (万十).
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.62,0:19:49.75,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,Ah… uhm…{NOTE:え…えっと…}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.75,0:19:52.79,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,Thanks, but more importantly,\Ncould you teach us what we need to know?{NOTE:それより私たちに教えてくれませんか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.79,0:19:54.71,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,About the Rite of Channeling that is.{NOTE:伝承の儀のことを。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.71,0:19:55.96,Default,Riddlemaster,0,0,0,,Okay.{NOTE:うん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.96,0:19:57.67,Default,Riddlemaster,0,0,0,,Follow me.{NOTE:ついてくるダ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.17,0:20:04.59,Default,Riddlemaster,0,0,0,,Each monster has kinship genes.{NOTE:モンスターはそれぞれ絆遺伝子というものを持ってるダ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.59,0:20:06.76,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,Kinship genes?{NOTE:絆遺伝子？}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.76,0:20:11.94,Default,Riddlemaster,0,0,0,,It's a gene that engraves the abilities and attributes of monsters.{NOTE:モンスターが持つ能力や属性が刻まれた遺伝子ダ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.94,0:20:16.69,Default,Riddlemaster,0,0,0,,In the beginning, a monster has all the kinship genes…{NOTE:そもそもモンスターは全ての絆遺伝子を持っているが…}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.69,0:20:20.69,Default,Riddlemaster,0,0,0,,…but most of their abilities remain asleep.{NOTE:…たいていの能力は眠ったままだべ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.69,0:20:24.66,Default,Riddlemaster,0,0,0,,But by hybridizing the bonds…{NOTE:だども絆と絆を掛け合わせることで…}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.66,0:20:28.70,Default,Riddlemaster,0,0,0,,…you can awaken their sleeping power.{NOTE:…眠れる力を目覚めさせることができる。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.70,0:20:31.50,Default,Riddlemaster,0,0,0,,That is the Rite of Channeling.{NOTE:それが伝承の儀ダ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.50,0:20:32.71,Default,(unison),0,0,0,,Oh.{NOTE:お。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.71,0:20:36.63,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,If Navirou was to undergo that Rite of Channeling,\Nwould I grow stronger too?{NOTE:伝承の儀をすればナビルーもさらに強くなれるのか!?}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.63,0:20:40.34,Default,Riddlemaster,0,0,0,,There are as many possibilities as there are monsters.{NOTE:可能性はモンスターの数だけあるダ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.34,0:20:42.42,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,Is it really possible?{NOTE:本当にそんなことが？}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.42,0:20:45.68,Default,Riddlemaster,0,0,0,,A picture is worth a thousand words.{NOTE:百聞は一見にしかずだべ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.68,0:20:48.18,Default,Riddlemaster,0,0,0,,Why don't you see for yourselves?{NOTE:その目で確かめるダ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.18,0:20:49.18,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,What's that?{NOTE:それは？}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.18,0:20:50.93,Default,Riddlemaster,0,0,0,,It's a Channeling Gem.{NOTE:絆珠だべ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.93,0:20:52.23,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,Channeling Gem?{NOTE:絆珠？}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.23,0:20:56.35,Default,Riddlemaster,0,0,0,,It is a mysterious orb that keeps the kinship genes.{NOTE:絆遺伝子が秘められている不思議な珠だべ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.35,0:21:02.82,Default,Riddlemaster,0,0,0,,This Channeling Gem that I'm holding contains kinship genes of a certain monster.{NOTE:この絆珠にはとあるモンスターの絆遺伝子が込められているダ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.82,0:21:04.51,Default,Riddlemaster,0,0,0,,Come here.{NOTE:ここに来るダ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.91,0:21:14.83,Default,Riddlemaster,0,0,0,,Now hold out your Kinship Stone.{NOTE:ほれ絆石を掲げるダ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.83,0:21:16.83,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,Eh, my Stone?{NOTE:えっ？絆石を？}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.83,0:21:18.63,Default,Riddlemaster,0,0,0,,Yep. Yep!{NOTE:んダんダ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.38,0:21:27.55,Default,Riddlemaster,0,0,0,,What is it, what is it?{NOTE:な～んダ何ダ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.55,0:21:30.18,Default,Riddlemaster,0,0,0,,What is the Channeling?{NOTE:伝承何ダ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.18,0:21:34.18,Default,Riddlemaster,0,0,0,,What does it mean to combine the kinship of two?{NOTE:二つの絆を合わせてできるのな～んダ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.56,0:21:36.27,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,Oh?{NOTE:ん？}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.52,0:21:43.24,Default,Riddlemaster,0,0,0,,It's waking up the sleeping power.{NOTE:眠れる力よ目覚めるダ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.70,0:21:49.91,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,Oh…{NOTE:おぉ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.38,0:22:03.67,Default,Riddlemaster,0,0,0,,Do you know which monster was it?{NOTE:どのモンスターか分かったダ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.88,0:22:06.13,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,Congalala?{NOTE:ババコンガ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.13,0:22:07.26,Default,Riddlemaster,0,0,0,,Correct.{NOTE:正解ダ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.26,0:22:08.09,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,Nya-ow!{NOTE:ニャグ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.09,0:22:09.32,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,Congalala!?{NOTE:ババコンガ!?}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.55,0:22:14.72,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,I don't need the kinship genes of a Congalala!{NOTE:ババコンガの絆遺伝子はいらニャ～イ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.48,0:22:21.77,Default,Riddlemaster,0,0,0,,If you want to awaken new Monsties powers…{NOTE:オトモンの新たなる力を目覚めさせたいのなら…}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.77,0:22:26.24,Default,Riddlemaster,0,0,0,,…you'll need to learn how to recharge\Nthis Channeling Gem with power.{NOTE:…この絆珠に力を込める修業をするダ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.24,0:22:27.90,Default,Riddlemaster,0,0,0,,Which one of you is going to take it?{NOTE:どっちが受け取るダ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.37,0:22:31.39,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,Cheval…?{NOTE:シュヴァル…}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.83,0:22:32.74,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{NOTE:うん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.64,0:22:57.06,Default,Avinia,0,0,0,,Frostfang…{NOTE:ヒョウガ…}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.56,0:23:01.15,Default,Avinia,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.{NOTE:ごめんね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.15,0:23:03.40,Default,Avinia,0,0,0,,I got us into this mess.{NOTE:つらい思いをさせて。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.40,0:23:06.11,Default,Avinia,0,0,0,,But I'm going to rescue you from this place.{NOTE:必ずここからあなたを助け出す。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.11,0:23:07.28,Default,Avinia,0,0,0,,I promise.{NOTE:約束よ。}
